# =============================================================================
# .gitignore — Sat_Kon Solution
# .NET 8 · ASP.NET Core Web API · Clean Architecture
# Generated for: Domain / Application / Infrastructure / Sat_Kon (API host)
# =============================================================================


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# .NET BUILD ARTIFACTS
# The bin/ and obj/ folders are produced by every project in the solution
# (Domain, Application, Infrastructure, Sat_Kon).  They are fully
# reproducible via 'dotnet build' and must never be committed.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/bin/
**/obj/

# NuGet local package cache (restored via 'dotnet restore')
packages/
*.nupkg
*.snupkg

# dotnet CLI tool manifests are repo-specific and should be committed,
# but the tool install cache should not.
.tools/

# Publish output (generated by 'dotnet publish')
**/publish/
**/out/


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# VISUAL STUDIO
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.userprefs
*.pidb
*.booproj
_ReSharper*/
*.DotSettings.user
[Ll]ocal.testsettings
TestResult.xml

# VS Code
.vscode/
!.vscode/extensions.json
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/tasks.json

# JetBrains Rider
.idea/
*.sln.iml

# Visual Studio Profiler
*.psess
*.vsp
*.vspx
*.sap


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TEST RESULTS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
[Tt]est[Rr]esult*/
[Bb]uild[Ll]og.*
*.VisualState.xml
*.coverage
*.coveragexml
coverage/
coverage-report/


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SECRETS & ENVIRONMENT FILES
#
# ⚠ SECURITY CRITICAL:
#   appsettings.json is tracked — it contains the config STRUCTURE and safe
#   defaults (log levels, Issuer, Audience names, etc.).
#
#   appsettings.Development.json is EXCLUDED because it may contain local
#   dev-only overrides.
#
#   The actual JWT signing keys (Jwt:AdminKey, Jwt:UserKey) and the
#   production database password that currently live in appsettings.json
#   MUST be moved to Azure App Service Application Settings / Key Vault
#   before the first production deployment. See the Docker deployment report.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
appsettings.Development.json
appsettings.Local.json
appsettings.*.local.json
secrets.json
**/*secrets*.json
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# User secrets (dotnet user-secrets) — stored outside the repo by design
# %APPDATA%\Microsoft\UserSecrets\  (Windows)
# ~/.microsoft/usersecrets/         (Linux/macOS)


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AZURE DEPLOYMENT & PUBLISH PROFILES
# Publish profiles contain server credentials and deployment settings.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.PublishSettings
**/Properties/PublishProfiles/*.pubxml
!**/Properties/PublishProfiles/*.pubxml.user
*.azurewebsites.net.publishsettings
*.publishproj
ServiceFabricBackup/
PublishScripts/


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# LOGS & TEMPORARY FILES
# The app writes logs to disk; none of these should be versioned.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
logs/
*.log
*.log.*
log/
temp/
tmp/
*.tmp
*.temp
*.bak
*.swp
*.cache
nohup.out


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DOCKER — BUILD ARTIFACTS ONLY
# The Dockerfile and .dockerignore ARE tracked (they are source files).
# Only generated Docker layer caches and override files are excluded.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
docker-compose.override.yml
.docker/


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# NODE.JS / FRONTEND
# The project's wwwroot currently holds uploads/videos/excels (runtime data,
# not source files). If a JS/TS frontend is added in future, these apply.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
dist/
build/
.next/
.nuxt/
.cache/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
yarn.lock
package-lock.json
.pnp.*
.pnp.js


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# WWWROOT — RUNTIME USER DATA
# These folders are populated at runtime (file uploads, generated reports,
# streamed videos). They are NOT source files and can be very large.
# In production they must live on an Azure Files share, not in Git.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/wwwroot/uploads/
**/wwwroot/videos/
**/wwwroot/excels/


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SQL SCRIPTS (development / migration scratch files)
# The one-off SQLQuery3.sql in the root is a dev artefact.
# Track only deliberate migration scripts if you add an EF Migrations folder.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
SQLQuery*.sql
*.sql.bak


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OS-GENERATED FILES
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# macOS
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes

# Windows
Thumbs.db
Thumbs.db:encryptable
ehthumbs.db
ehthumbs_vista.db
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/
*.lnk

# Linux
*~


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ENTITY FRAMEWORK CORE — MIGRATION SNAPSHOTS
# The Migrations/ folder and ModelSnapshot SHOULD be committed so the team
# shares a consistent migration history. Nothing to exclude here — listed
# for clarity so developers do not accidentally add them to .gitignore.
#
#   ✔ Migrations/         → TRACKED
#   ✔ *ModelSnapshot.cs   → TRACKED
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# FILES EXPLICITLY KEPT TRACKED
# (These negation rules protect key files even if a parent pattern matches.)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
!Dockerfile
!.dockerignore
!.gitignore
!.editorconfig
!**/*.csproj
!**/*.slnx
!**/*.sln
!**/appsettings.json
!**/appsettings.Production.json
!.github/
!.github/**
